{"id":141288,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：东京为婴儿发放瓶装水/","date":"2011-03-25T09:00:20Z","modified":"2011-03-25T09:00:20Z","title":"简讯：东京为婴儿发放瓶装水","content":"<div>\n<p>日本东京发现自来水辐射超标后，星期四（3月24日）开始为婴儿发放瓶装水。</p>\n<p>东京都政府当日早晨开始分发24万瓶饮用水。</p>\n<p>东京都葛饰区金町自来水净化厂检测到每升水的放射性碘为210贝克勒尔。超过婴儿100贝克勒尔的标准值。</p>\n<p>成人的放射性碘安全标准值是每升300贝克勒尔。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/7N83CXd6gmhnSurPk9kgbNJ2zCE/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/7N83CXd6gmhnSurPk9kgbNJ2zCE/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/7N83CXd6gmhnSurPk9kgbNJ2zCE/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/7N83CXd6gmhnSurPk9kgbNJ2zCE/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/aHhVmWEU_80\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):gongminshehui1ATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}